title: TOT Stadium Chaeng Watthana
text: TOT Stadium Chaeng Watthana () is a football stadium in <a href="Lak%20Si%20District">Lak Si</a>, <a href="Bangkok">Bangkok</a>, <a href="Thailand">Thailand</a>. It is used for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches at several competitions and levels and was the home stadium of <a href="TOT%20S.C.">TOT Sport Club</a>, which was dissolved in 2016. The stadium holds 5,000 spectators.
